(1810, 177, 'about_sub_tittle', '<span> Jolly International Group of Companies </span> was established in 1988 with the aim of capitalizing on <br> the Philippines rapid social and economic growth, the ongoing enhancement of living standards, the substantial demand within the Philippine market, the deepening ties between the Philippines and China, and the growing business prospects for overseas Chinese entrepreneurs in the Philippines. Over the course of 35 years, the company has consistently expanded its product range, broadened its business horizons, and continually refined its operational processes. Presently, the group employs thousands of individuals and operates across various sectors, including plastic products, sponge mattresses, real estate development residential, industrial, commercial, construction, commercial mixing stations, animal feed production, cement bricks, and more. Each business division operates as an independent subsidiary, ensuring efficient functioning and resource sharing.'),
